 measurement of the mass function. Finally, we comment on the\nsignificance of our results for relativistic-jet and core-collapse models, and\nfor the detection of gravitational waves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Jun 2006 20:47:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Aug 2006 19:58:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
